Paranormal Underground  - January until May (2010)
English | PDF

At Paranormal Underground, our primary goal is to explore the unexplained from all angles. To do this, we present stories about the paranormal, talk to top paranormal researchers, present personal paranormal experiences, offer round table debates about paranormal issues, and track paranormal news. We provide coverage of all aspects of the paranormal, including ghosts, cryptids, UFOs, unexplained phenomena, conspiracies, haunted sites, and more.
